Folders
    k8s/ - Kubernetes configuration files (deployment, service, ingress, etc.) for container orchestration.
    
    migrations/ – Database migration scripts (e.g., TypeORM or Sequelize) to manage schema changes.

    src/ – Main application source code (controllers, services, modules, entities, etc.).

    test/ – Unit, integration, or e2e test files


Files
.env.example – Template for environment variables (copy to .env and fill in real values).

Dockerfile – Instructions to build a Docker image for the application.

Jenkinsfile – Pipeline definition for CI/CD using Jenkins.

nest-cli.json – Configuration for NestJS CLI (project structure, compiler options).

package.json – Lists dependencies, scripts, and project metadata (npm/yarn).

tsconfig.json – TypeScript compiler settings..